No. 932 No. 933

(October Term, 1930).

Art Metal Construction Co. v. United States; and Zeller et al. v. Same.

(October Term, 1930).

May 8, 1933.

The mo*707tions for leave to file petitions for rehearing in the above-entitled causes are severally denied. Bronson v. Schulten, 104 U.S. 410, 415; United States v. Mayer, 235 U.S. 55, 67.

Messrs. Dana B. Hellings, Frederick C. Slee, and Ralph Ulsh for the applicants. For previous decisions, see 283 U.S. 863; 47 F. (2d) 558; and 46 F. (2d) 1023.
